        public Gym(String nameOfGym,
           MembershipType[] membershipTypes,
           Double[] membershipRates,
           double personalTrainerRate)
        Construct a gym from the specified parameters. Validates parameter values and substitutes defaults if any are invalid.
        Parameters:
        nameOfGym - the name of the gym; must be no more than 20 characters
        membershipTypes - the types of memberships for the gym
        membershipRates - the rates corresponding to the membershipTypes
        personalTrainerRate - the rate for one hour with a personal trainer

    • Method Detail

      • addMember

        public void addMember(String firstName,
                      String lastName,
                      MembershipType typeOfMember,
                      int hoursQ1,
                      int hoursQ2,
                      int hoursQ3,
                      int hoursQ4)
        Create and add a new member to this gym. This adds a new member to a gym's list of members. The hoursQ1 through hoursQ4 parameters provide the number of personal trainer hours that the member paid for in each quarter of the year.
        Parameters:
        firstName - the first name of the member
        lastName - the last name of the member
        typeOfMember - the membership type of the member
        hoursQ1 - the number of hours for Q1
        hoursQ2 - the number of hours for Q2
        hoursQ3 - the number of hours for Q3
        hoursQ4 - the number of hours for Q4

        Parameters:

      • createAnnualReport

        public String createAnnualReport()
        Create the annual report for this gym. This method returns a String, suitable for display on the console, with the names of each of the members and the amount of money they paid. The string returned must contain one line for each member. Each line shows the member, using Member.toString(), followed by the total amount of money that member paid for the year. For example, 
         Name: Stan Lem spent $718.40
 Name: Agatha Kristy spent $1,590.58
 Name: Lee Jones spent $48.00
        Returns:
        the annual report as a displayable string

      • highestTrainingHours

        public Member highestTrainingHours()
        Determine and return the member with the highest number of training hours. This method goes through the list of all members and returns the member that has the highest number of personal training hours for the year.
        Returns:
        the member with the highest training hours

      • calculateTotalTrainingHours

        public int calculateTotalTrainingHours()
        Calculate the total number of training hours of all members of this gym. This method sums up all the personal training hours for the gym for the four quarters and returns that total.
        Returns:
        the total number of training hours
